WEBVTT

00:02.458 --> 00:06.709
Maple trees like this one

00:02.458 --> 00:06.709
store sap in their trunks.

00:06.750 --> 00:09.417
We use a pump

00:06.750 --> 00:09.417
to draw the liquid out.

00:09.458 --> 00:10.625
( click )

