Maple sap is mainly water,

00:19.583 --> 00:23.208
so we need this machine

00:23.250 --> 00:24.834
to remove most of the moisture--

00:24.875 --> 00:28.333
Leaving pure

00:24.875 --> 00:28.333
maple syrup! Yum.

00:28.375 --> 00:31.834
You refuse carrot soup,

00:28.375 --> 00:31.834
yet you enjoy this plant liquid.

00:31.875 --> 00:34.375
Because it's awesome

00:31.875 --> 00:34.375
