00:42.875 --> 00:47.583
Welcome to the annual

00:42.875 --> 00:47.583
Griffin Rock Syrup Harvest!

00:47.625 --> 00:49.667
Huxley,

00:47.625 --> 00:49.667
are you getting this?

00:49.709 --> 00:52.625
Of course,

00:49.709 --> 00:52.625
Mayor Luskey!

00:52.667 --> 00:54.417
Because nothing says

00:52.667 --> 00:54.417
prime time anchor

00:54.458 --> 00:56.542
like watching

00:54.458 --> 00:56.542
the sap run.

00:56.583 --> 00:58.583
(  dramatic theme playing  )

01:04.875 --> 01:06.542
Chief Burns!

01:06.583 --> 01:09.375
Ugh. This guy.

01:09.417 --> 01:11.417
Have you given any more

01:09.417 --> 01:11.417
thought to participating

01:11.458 --> 01:15.625
in my reality show?

01:11.458 --> 01:15.625
I have the perfect title...

01:15.667 --> 01:19.291
Huxley Prescott's Bots!

01:20.500 --> 01:21.750
Bots?

01:21.792 --> 01:23.834
A TV series about us?

01:23.875 --> 01:26.458
They're not your Bots,

01:23.875 --> 01:26.458
Mr. Prescott,

01:26.500 --> 01:28.500
and my answer is still no.

01:28.542 --> 01:30.458
Rescue work is dangerous.

01:30.500 --> 01:33.375
That's what makes it

01:30.500 --> 01:33.375
great TV!

01:33.417 --> 01:35.333
( light applause )

01:35.375 --> 01:38.583
Yeah, all right,

01:35.375 --> 01:38.583
all right. Simmer.

01:38.625 --> 01:42.583
I'm happy to pour

01:38.625 --> 01:42.583
from this season's first bottle

01:42.625 --> 01:45.291
of liquid gold!

01:45.333 --> 01:46.959
( chuckles )

01:47.000 --> 01:48.917
( crowd cheers )

01:51.542 --> 01:53.000
Whoa! Oh no!

01:53.667 --> 01:54.959
Showtime!

01:55.000 --> 01:57.000
